=3D"TopicPara_topicText__CUB0d">Time:</span></i><span data-testid=3D"topicT=
ext" class=3D"TopicPara_topicText__CUB0d"> It takes about 8 minutes to smok=
e a cigarette plus time to earn money to purchase that cigarette and find a=
 place to smoke it. Because many places have adopted smoke-free policies, f=
inding a smoking-friendly spot is not as easy as it used to be. As a result=
, a person who smokes one pack a day may end up devoting about 3 hours each=
